myapp.GUIfx.Admin

Class AdminController

  • java.lang.Object
    • myapp.GUIfx.Admin.AdminController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable

    public class AdminController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    The AdminController is the controller of AdminPane.fxml. The class contains methods to fill the AdminPane with information. It also contains methods to log out, see other admins contact information, register new admins and change the users own information.

    Sara Hjelle
